headline: BofA Returns to Cintas (CTAS) Coverage, Highlighting Steady Industry Fundamentals
summary: Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS) is included among the 13 Best Performing Long Term Stocks to Invest in. On February 17, BofA analyst Curtis Nagle reinstated coverage of Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS). The analyst reiterated a Neutral rating and a $215 price target. The move came as the firm resumed coverage of 19 Information and Business Services stocks. […]
